Acts 7-42 But <f>ⓑ</f>God turned away and <f>ⓒ</f>gave them over to worship <f>ⓓ</f>the host of heaven, as it is written in the book of the prophets: <pb/><t><f>ⓔ</f>“‘Did you bring to me slain beasts and sacrifices, </t><t><f>ⓕ</f>during the forty years in the wilderness, O house of Israel?</t>
